--- /workspace/server.py
+++ /workspace/server.py
@@ -0,0 +1,4 @@
+#!/usr/bin/env python3
+import http.server
+import socketserver
+import os
@@ -1,0 +6,14 @@
+class CustomHandler(http.server.SimpleHTTPRequestHandler):
+    def do_GET(self):
+        if self.path == "/" or self.path == "/candidate_dashboard.html":
+            self.path = "/candidate_dashboard.html"
+        return super().do_GET()
+
+if __name__ == "__main__":
+    # Ensure the working directory is the directory of this script
+    os.chdir(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)))
+    PORT = 6060
+    with socketserver.TCPServer(("", PORT), CustomHandler) as httpd:
+        print(f"Serving candidate_dashboard.html at http://localhost:{PORT}/")
+        httpd.serve_forever()
+
